        public OrganismPost(double x,
                    double y,

        Creates a new organism representation with given values
        Parameters:
        organismType - Type of organism to create, as determined by Organism.getTypeNumber()
        x - X position
        y - Y position
        food - Current amount of food. For organisms that don't need food (trees, moss) this value doesn't matter
        reproductionTimer - Current index in reproduction count.
